### `ExtractedImage`

Image extracted from document.

```rust
pub struct ExtractedImage {
    /// Raw image bytes
    pub data: Bytes,

    /// Format: "jpeg", "png", "webp", etc.
    pub format: Cow<'static, str>,

    /// Zero-indexed position
